Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.09,0:00:05.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,およそ遠しとされしもの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,下等で奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:13.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見慣れた動植物とはまるで違うと思しきもの達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それら異形の一群を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:20.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人は古くから畏れを含み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:23.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつしか総じて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:25.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「蟲」と呼んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:16.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:25.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,シゲル　あそこ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山に　取られたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イボ診てくれるってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:13.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,蟲師だって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お医者じゃないのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こいつはいつ頃から？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:27.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この三日の内に皆が急にです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,足がしびれて辛いそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,皆困っております
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:37.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰かが山に入ったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから死が伝染ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:42.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,死が伝染る？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,四日前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,亡くなった者がありましてな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この里では　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:04:01.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの山のあちこちにある沼地に死者を置いて葬るのです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,するとやがて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:09.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,骸は骨まで消えて　衣のみとなる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:15.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山へ帰るのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々は思っております
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:22.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ですが　それが終わるまで　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:26.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,七日間は山へ入ってはならんのです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:33.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,遠い昔　それを破った者が病を持ち帰り
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:38.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,里じゅうに広めたという言い伝えがあるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:43.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それゆえ皆　恐れておるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:49.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは　「骸草」の芽か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:57.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,動物の骸を骨まで分解して　泥状にする蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:03.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その泥を生体に踏まれる事で　子株を広げ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:08.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それを　また踏んだ生体に寄生してゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,言い伝えとも重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,間違いないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これを　試してみてください
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,取れた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:39.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イボが取れたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しびれも治った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:56.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あった　これだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:06:00.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,草全体には　塩を…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あのう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前さんも薬がいるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:23.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,伯父さんを　診てあげて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,抜いても抜いても　生えてくるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,抜くと手にまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,薬が効かない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,他の者と明らかに違う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山に入ったのはあんたか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:07.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,死んだのは　俺の弟でな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この子と山へ供養に行ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何故掟を破ってまで？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんな言い伝えは嘘だと思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,十年前　俺の娘がいなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:33.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,捜すと山で衣だけが見つかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:37.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,皆　山に取られたのだと言った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:44.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　思えば　山に入った誰も病にはならなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:48.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから　大丈夫だと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:53.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,弟さんの骸が　山に帰るところを見たのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:11.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さんに　会いたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:16.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山に　ひとりにするなんて　かわいそうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:24.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう一度　お別れを言いに行くか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ　この草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:48.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このっ　このっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さん　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:10.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当にもう山の一部になったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:19.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この草　父さんの分を　生きてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:33.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ　もう戻ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ひとりになってしまったな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　うちの子供になるか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おじさんを父さんの代わりと思ってくれ　な？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:53.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ　帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう　泣くな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:05.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その日以来　足から草の芽が生えてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,日に日に育っている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:11.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妙だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:17.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山で偶然　泥状の骸を踏み　病となった例は割りとある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　どれも薬で難なく治っている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何が違う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,骸と血縁があるという事か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　なら甥も条件は同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何か原因は他にある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:41.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,故意に骸のある場所へ行き　泥を踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,供養に行った者の足に泥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,弟さんはどんな亡くなり方を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,草介　お前は外へ行っておいで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,崖から落ちてな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,打ち所が悪かったか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見つかった時にはもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:19.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつはいつも　俺を慕ってくれてた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:23.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,特別　仲のいい兄弟だったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辛かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,伯父さん　治った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:39.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　まだわからん事があってな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前さんも　薬塗っとくか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おれはいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:49.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この草
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さんの代わりに生えてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも辛いだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:00.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,親父さんもお前さんを苦しめたくはないんじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:08.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　まだ無理なら　薬は伯父さんに預けとく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:11.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その気になったら　使うといい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:21.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,な　親父さんと伯父さんとはどんな兄弟だった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:29.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さんは伯父さんのこと　大好きだったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:34.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,小さい頃はよく伯父さんとの思い出話をしてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　何年か前から
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あまり伯父さんのこと話さなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:08.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,兄さん　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,兄さん　話したいことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ　シノブ　思い詰めた顔して　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何でも言えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,兄さん　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:56.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユリは　俺が死なせてしまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユリがいると知らずに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,荷車の下敷きに…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:10.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,兄さんに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,言えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:19.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そのまま山へ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すまない　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:29.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,兄さん　すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:39.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺も　子を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子を見るたび苦しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:51.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしてこんなことを…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:45.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,兄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もういい　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もういい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は死んだんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:23.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　まだ生きてるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:39.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,草介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:49.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さんは昔ある人にひどいことをしてしまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もしも父さんに何かあっても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:59.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は誰も恨んだりしないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:08.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何　この里の者はいつかは皆山に帰るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:15.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何も心配することはない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:31.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一つ考えが浮かびましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　試しに聞いてみてください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その足に生えているのは　骸草という蟲だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,普段は泥状のものだが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:48.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,生き物の屍臭に反応し　死骸から芽を出す
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:52.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その芽を踏むと寄生されるが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:55.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,生きたものから芽を出しても育つことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:01.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　あんたのは骸と同じ反応をしている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:08.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたの体に屍臭が染みついているからと考えると筋が通る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:16.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体　何のことを言っている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それを追及するつもりはない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この考えが正しければ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,僅かな屍臭も残さぬよう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しっかりと洗い清めれば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,薬も効くようになるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,心当たりがあるなら　試してみるといい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:39.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺が口を出すのはここまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:16.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さんを殺したの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:21.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何を言ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:26.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,聞いてたんだ　さっきの蟲師さんの話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:34.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そのことを誰かに言ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ううん　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺　誰にも言わないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:50.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さんは誰も恨むなって言ったから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:55.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,伯父さんは俺に優しくしてくれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なのにどうして　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなことしてしまったの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:09.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,怒りでどうしようもなくなってな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:16.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だがもし　あの時堪えられたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:21.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どの道いつかはこうなってただろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前だっていつかは俺を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:39.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,足が…草介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:44.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,早く　助け…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だこりゃ　踏んじまった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:17.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,下見て歩けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:32.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山へも帰れなかったのか
